{
  "stem": "3382.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't because--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Abraham Melezin, A-B-R-A-H-A-M M-E-L-E-Z-I-N, N like 'Nancy.'",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During, during the war, when I left the ghetto and I went on so-called Aryan side, I used the name Adam Mielzynski, A-D-A-M M-I-E-L-Z-Y-N-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] The next Thursday I'll be 85.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born on June 29, 1910, in Odessa, then Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "O-D-E-S-S-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, my memories go very far back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do you-- do you imagine that I remember how my sister was born, and they moved my crib from one corner and put it in that place, her crib?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father came probably from a small town or Ukrainian shtetl Znamenka.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that he was a tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he made good in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Besides the shop, we had something-- another-- together with the tailor shop, there was also a store, where he used to sell ready-to-make or ready-order suits.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I remember where my mother or the nanny would take me there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I remember the shop with counter and materials, and whatever or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in the back room-- some three or four sewing machines and bearded Jewish men in their typical caps, you know, chewing something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was a woman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometimes, I saw some kind of a child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And obviously he made good because in my birth certificate, I remember, it was written that [NON-ENGLISH] Abraham, Abraham, son of Eliezer, son of so-so, Merchant of the First Guild.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the First Guild was something that the passport-- that who-- you could travel all over Russia, even to Moscow and St.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Petersburg, which essentially was beyond the Jewish pale.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you could do that only-- you could go there only with special permits from the authorities.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
